Detailed Description

Interface definition for the RegisterResult elements.

The <RegisterResult> is used by the X-KRSS service to response to a user request to register a new key with the service.

The schema definition for RegisterResult is as follows :

   <!-- RegisterResult -->
   <element name="RegisterResult" type="xkms:RegisterResultType"/>
   <complexType name="RegisterResultType">
      <complexContent>
         <extension base="xkms:ResultType">
            <sequence>
               <element ref="xkms:KeyBinding" minOccurs="0" 
                     maxOccurs="unbounded"/>
               <element ref="xkms:PrivateKey" minOccurs="0"/>
            </sequence>
         </extension>
      </complexContent>
   </complexType>
   <!-- /RegisterResult -->
